    "instruction": "Load metric.csv, trace.csv, log.csv, and error_logs.csv. For each file, return a compact summary: total row count, list of unique cmdb_id values (sorted), and up to 20 unique KPI/trace/log names (for metric.csv use kpi_name, for trace.csv use trace_name, for log.csv use log_name, for error_logs.csv return up to 20 distinct message samples). Also report the minimum and maximum timestamp (as Unix seconds) found in each file. Keep outputs concise (limit lists to 20 items). Do not filter by time window yet."
